Package mklab.JGNN.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Distribution
    This interface abstracts a probability distribution passed that can be passed to Tensor.setToRandom(Distribution) for random tensor initialization.
    Optimizer
    Provides an interface for training tensors.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LSTM  
    LSTM.LSTMState  
    Matrix
    This class provides an abstract implementation of Matrix functionalities.
    Model
    This class is a way to organize NNOperation trees into trainable machine learning models.
    ModelBuilder
    This class and subclasses can be used to create Model instances by automatically creating and managing NNOperations based on textual descriptions.
    NNOperation
    This class defines an abstract neural network operation with forward and backpropagation capabilities.
    Tensor
    This class provides a native java implementation of Tensor functionalities.
    ThreadPool
    This class provides a thread manager that automatically schedules threaded runables so that the total number of threads running at a given time does not exceed the number of available processors.
